title: Hour 3 - Aaron Judge Triple Crown Chase, Ben Simmons Laughs It Off
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Aaron Judge Triple Crown Chase, Ben Simmons Laughs It Off
description:
Dan and the Danettes wonder who will be the pitcher who gives up New York Yankees slugger Aaron Judge's 62nd HR. And Dan shows concern for Brooklyn Nets PG Ben Simmons, who seems to be laughing off his struggles.
